OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772647566
OL,3,CRugby League side reinstated with 12-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,FRugby League in Halifax has been
OL,7,Fhanded a reprieve as the Rugby
OL,8,FFootball League today granted
OL,9,Fmembership of the 2026 Betfred
OL,10,FChampionship to a new Halifax Panthers
OL,11,Fclub.
OL,13,FHaving been a member of the RFL for
OL,14,F153 years, the second-tier side faced
OL,15,Fliquidation in the High Court in
OL,16,FFebruary and had their league
OL,17,Fmembership removed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772647566
OL,3,CRugby League side reinstated with 12-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,FThis forced the postponement of
OL,7,Ffixtures against Sheffield Eagles and
OL,8,FBarrow Raiders and also meant all
OL,9,Fplayers were free to move to other
OL,10,Fclubs.
OL,12,FA decision was made at an RFL Board
OL,13,Fmeeting after what the governing body
OL,14,Fcalled "extensive work from a number
OL,15,Fof parties and a detailed application
OL,16,Ffrom the directors of the new entity."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772647566
OL,3,CRugby League side reinstated with 12-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,FRFL interim chief executive Abi Ekoku,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We understand the trauma to
OL,8,Fplayers, staff and fans in recent
OL,9,Fweeks; but remained hopeful that the
OL,10,Fclub would have a chance of survival.
OL,11,FThat has proved to be the case,
OL,12,Fprimarily down to an exceptional
OL,13,Fcommunity, corporate and political
OL,14,Feffort."
OL,16,FIt does however mean the new outfit
OL,17,Fwill have a delayed start to their
OL,18,Fseason with a 12-point deduction. The
OL,19,Ffixtures against Sheffield and Barrow
OL,20,Fwill be rescheduled.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
