FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772647566
OL,3,CRugby League side reinstated with 12-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,FLocal businessman Martyn Buchan has
OL,7,Fled negotiations with the RFL and
OL,8,Fcalled the decision a great relief. He
OL,9,Fsaid:
OL,11,F"Thanks to all the invested staff,
OL,12,Fsponsors, the governing body and the
OL,13,FCalderdale Council who have helped
OL,14,Fmake it possible for this to happen.
OL,16,FThe club has five new directors in
OL,17,FAdam Butterfield, Jason Clough,
OL,18,FChristopher Brooke, Benjamin Walker
OL,19,Fand John Coulter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
